This is a list of artists that have reached number - one on the UK Singles Chart as recorded by the Official Charts Company .
Artists are listed alphabetically and separately if more than one artist is credited on a song ( e.g. 
Artists who performed on a song but not credited are not included although notable cases may be recorded in the Notes column .
In the 20th century guest musicians or singers were sometimes credited and sometimes not , while it became more common to include featured artists in the early 21st century .
This list covers all chart weeks up to the week ending 10 September 2015 .
